content: So when I say things feel like they're slowing down, I'm not saying we don't have a lot of activity, we just don't have as much as I would typically expect in the fourth quarter. But that's just where someone -- if you have a business and you have 2,000 to 6,000, 7,000 feet and you got to guarantee the lease, you're going to go, okay, I'm comfortable for the next five years, I'm not comfortable beyond that.
